# Testing Standards

## Framework
- Use Bun's built-in test runner: `import { test, expect, describe, mock } from 'bun:test'`
- No Jest, no Vitest — Bun test is the single test runner

## What to Test
- Backend services: unit test each service method with mocked AzureDevOpsClient
- Permission decoder: test bitmask logic exhaustively with known values
- Identity resolver: test descriptor mapping with fixture data
- Graph builder: integration test with full mocked AzDO responses
- Frontend: test Zustand store actions and React Query hook behavior

## Mocking AzDO Client
- Always mock `AzureDevOpsClient` at the module level in service tests
- Never make real HTTP calls in tests — use fixture JSON files in `tests/fixtures/`
- Fixture files mirror real AzDO API response shapes exactly

## Coverage Goals (POC)
- Services: 80% line coverage minimum
- Utils/constants: 100%
- Routes: happy path + error cases
- Frontend components: smoke tests only for POC

## Test File Location
- Backend: `apps/backend/src/__tests__/{service}.test.ts`
- Frontend: co-located with component: `GraphCanvas.test.tsx` next to `GraphCanvas.tsx`